---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const baseN = base.replace(/\/$/, "");
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Kapitola — pripravujeme"
  description="The chapter — Phase 4 deliverable, drafting in 2028. Until then, see the hymn-pair dossier and source register for evidence and methodology."
  lang="sk"
>
  <section class="bg-ink-800 px-6 py-16 text-parchment">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-content text-center">
      <p class="font-sans text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold">
        Phase 4 / 2028 · Drafting deliverable
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-section-title font-display font-bold text-parchment-100">
        Kapitola
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-prose font-sans text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-parchment-500" lang="en">
        Hypertext Monograph Chapter
      </p>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-prose text-parchment-400">
        Monografická kapitola sa pripravuje v rámci grantu APVV-24-0484
        (TEPALIT) a je naplánovaná ako výstup Fázy 4 v roku 2028.
      </p>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-prose font-sans text-sm italic text-parchment-500" lang="en">
        The monograph chapter is in preparation under the APVV-24-0484
        (TEPALIT) grant and is scheduled as a Phase 4 deliverable in 2028.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-content px-6 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-section-title text-ink">Čo už je dostupné</h2>
    <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-sm italic text-ink-300" lang="en">
      What is already available
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-400">
      Kým kapitola nie je hotová, jej infraštruktúra a empirické jadro sú
      verejne prístupné a citovateľné cez tieto sekcie:
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-xs italic leading-relaxed text-ink-300" lang="en">
      Until the chapter is complete, its infrastructure and empirical core
      are publicly accessible and citable through these sections:
    </p>

    <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <li class="card">
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-ink">
          <a href={`${baseN}/hymn-pairs/`} class="hover:text-burgundy">
            Hymno-páry
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-xs italic text-ink-300" lang="en">
          Hymn-Pair Dossier
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-400">
          Empirické jadro kapitoly — päť aktívnych dossierov + jeden
          výskumný cieľ; dva sú VERIFIED.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-ink">
          <a href={`${baseN}/synoptikon/`} class="hover:text-burgundy">
            Synoptikon
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-xs italic text-ink-300" lang="en">
          Parallel Text Viewer
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-400">
          Paralelné porovnania konfesijných textov a hymnov.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-ink">
          <a href={`${baseN}/taxonomy/`} class="hover:text-burgundy">
            Teologická taxonómia
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-xs italic text-ink-300" lang="en">
          Theological Taxonomy
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-400">
          Štyri teologické loci × šesť sub-loci = 24 kategórií, na ktoré
          sa kapitola opiera.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-ink">
          <a href={`${baseN}/sources/`} class="hover:text-burgundy">
            Pramene
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-xs italic text-ink-300" lang="en">
          Source Register
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-400">
          Register kotviacich identifikátorov pre každý prameň, na ktorý
          sa kapitola odvoláva.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <div class="ornament-rule"></div>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-content px-6 py-12 pb-20">
    <h2 class="text-section-title text-ink">Citovať dataset</h2>
    <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-sm italic text-ink-300" lang="en">
      Cite the dataset
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-400">
      Kým kapitola nevyšla, cituje sa aktuálna verzia datasetu cez Zenodo
      DOI:
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-sm">
      <a
        href="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20081435"
        class="text-burgundy hover:underline"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20081435
      </a>
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-xs italic text-ink-300" lang="en">
      Each individual hymn-pair dossier on <a href={`${baseN}/hymn-pairs/`} class="text-burgundy">/hymn-pairs/</a> carries its own permalink and "How to cite this pair" snippet (APA + BibTeX).
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
